RESULTS
BY TOURNAMENT RESULTS OF HOST NATIONS Section::::Results of host nations .
Except in 1934 , host nations are granted an automatic spot in the World Cup group stage .
The first host ever to fail to advance past the first round was South Africa in 2010 .
† denotes the best result in the team 's history , ‡ - the best result at the time of the competition ( improved later ) . !
