+ List of UEFA193019341938195019541958196219661970197419781982198619901994199820022006201020142018 OVERALL Section::::Overall .
After the first twenty - one World Cups , all top 2 finishes , and all but two top 4 finishes , have been achieved by European ( UEFA ) and South American ( CONMEBOL ) countries .
The other four football regions together have got just one third place , won by the United States in the inaugural 1930 tournament , and one fourth place , won by South Korea on home soil in 2002 .
